# Today Meal UI Design System

- Style direction: premium, warm, healing, creamy, minimal. Prefer generous whitespace, rounded cards, soft shadows, and warm brown accents.
- Core colors: primary `#B7895C`, primary light `#F5EAE2`, primary dark/pressed `#9F6E46`, page background `#FFF8F5`, card background `#FFFFFF`, divider `#EFE7E1`.
- Text colors: primary `#2D2520`, secondary `#8C7F76`, tertiary `#C5BEB8`. Status colors: success `#5FB878`, alert/tip `#FF6B6B`.
- Typography: Chinese `PingFang SC`; English can use SF Pro/DIN style. In rpx: hero title `56rpx`, page title `40rpx`, module title `32rpx`, body `28rpx`, helper `24rpx`, button `28rpx`.
- Radius tokens in rpx: tag/small button `16rpx`, input/small card `24rpx`, main card `32rpx`, large image card `48rpx`, circle `50%`.
- Spacing uses a 4px base grid, so use multiples of `8rpx`. Page horizontal padding `32rpx`, card padding `32rpx`, module spacing around `48rpx`.
- Shadows: light `0 4rpx 24rpx rgba(45,37,32,0.06)`, medium `0 8rpx 40rpx rgba(45,37,32,0.08)`.
- Buttons: primary height about `96rpx`, radius `24rpx`, background primary, white text. Secondary height about `80rpx`, radius `24rpx`, primary border/text.
- TabBar: 5 items `首页 / 菜谱 / 随机 / 收藏 / 我的`; background white; selected primary, inactive secondary; center random button is a `112rpx` circle floating `24rpx` upward.
- Cards and lists: dish card radius `32rpx`, padding `32rpx`, image radius `24rpx`; list row target height around `176rpx`.
- Tags: height about `64rpx`, radius `32rpx`; selected uses primary-light background and primary text, inactive uses page background and secondary text.
- Product pages to preserve: home greeting, random recommendation card, quick recipe/takeout entries, inspiration horizontal list, filter chips, random result, recipe list, add form, and takeout favorites.
- UI review checklist before finishing miniapp changes: paired action buttons must use the same height and equal-width layout (`flex: 1 1 0; width: 0` or a 2-column grid); custom topbar titles must be single-line with `white-space: nowrap`; empty/simple pages need a hero/summary card plus clear primary action, not only one button on blank background.
- Custom topbar pages must reserve the native WeChat capsule area on the right; do not add a custom share button beside or under the capsule. Use `onShareAppMessage` and the native capsule menu for page sharing unless the user explicitly asks for an in-page share CTA.
- Form pages should keep submit/save actions as full-width primary buttons in the page content area, not as topbar icon buttons. Topbars should remain navigation-first: back, centered single-line title, and capsule-safe right spacing.
- Default/empty food images should use CSS placeholders or local assets, not third-party remote URLs. Only load remote images when they come from user uploads or saved backend data.
- For new pages, preserve hierarchy: topbar, contextual hero card, section header, content cards/list, then primary action. Avoid sparse pages that feel unfinished.
- Collaboration UI: show members with overlapping avatar stacks when space allows; avoid explanatory collaboration copy unless the user explicitly asks for it.
